{"tid":1524731,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"幫罷唔倒課嘅中學生諗諗點處理升旗禮","createTime":"2019-08-31T18:00:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T04:30:18.000Z","uid":130190,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"9fcd29311d1b07b20675bd644ab3030bc7a4481e","tid":1524731,"uid":130190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:00:56.000Z","msg":"好多學校開學日都會搞升（共匪）旗禮，同時有啲學生始終冇辦法/唔敢罷課<br />\n如果真係要面對升旗禮，全部反共同學仔有個統一動作表示抗爭會好啲<br />\n<br />\n遮右眼堅定眼神望前（唔望旗）？<br />\n擰轉身遮右眼？<br />\n其他？<br />\n<br />\n集思廣益<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2622a8f0fa92934af4f44553e27f2980dfa3f61e","tid":1524731,"uid":169207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:01:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mSpP8pQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmSpP8pQ.jpg&h=9426be84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wUD5GKS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwUD5GKS.jpg&h=5fe937c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KVvWOpU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKVvWOpU.jpg&h=ea761e81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BKfDhih.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBKfDhih.jpg&h=3f2dc27c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/A0xaSRE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FA0xaSRE.jpg&h=529769b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iQzkvDm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiQzkvDm.jpg&h=2d664012&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b8e78aa3546f1eb4388c2f40571fd3668e2b91ad","tid":1524731,"uid":130190,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T18:03:27.000Z","msg":"推呀<br />\n901機場見"},{"pid":"e02b208cc1c757bb5614692bbee1d8d14cf0cb77","tid":1524731,"uid":223468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score